cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SD 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) of crisis-related messages on Twitter. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves machine learning classifiers, which falls under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Information retrieval (cs.IR) is also relevant as the paper discusses the challenges of processing social media information. Additionally, the paper deals with crisis situations, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
